tool_description: Handles the database of the wallet
title: Felina Multisig Wallet API

api_list.name: Add transaction description
api_list.description: Stores a new description in the database.
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://felina-multisig-wallet-api.p.rapidapi.com/api/descriptions"

headers = {
    "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
    "X-RapidAPI-Host": "felina-multisig-wallet-api.p.rapidapi.com"
}

response = requests.post(url, headers=headers)

print(response.json())
